{
  "id": "5cc00002f384810017c1d8fc",
  "title": "「効果的なチームとは何か」を知る",
  "created": 1556086788,
  "updated": 1556098214,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5cc00002f384810017c1d8fc",
      "text": "「効果的なチームとは何か」を知る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556086788,
      "updated": 1556086788
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc00004aff09e000082ff10",
      "text": "[Google re:Work - ガイド: 「効果的なチームとは何か」を知る https://rework.withgoogle.com/jp/guides/understanding-team-effectiveness/steps/introduction/]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556086788,
      "updated": 1556086824
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc00026aff09e000082ff12",
      "text": "Googleがやった分析 [Project Aristotle]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556086824,
      "updated": 1556088289
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc00062aff09e000082ff14",
      "text": "\t「効果的なチームを可能とする条件は何か」を見つけるのが目的",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556086882,
      "updated": 1556086887
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc00068aff09e000082ff15",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556086889,
      "updated": 1556086889
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc0002caff09e000082ff13",
      "text": "[心理的安全性]という言葉がバズワードになるきっかけを作った",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556086829,
      "updated": 1556086846
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc00459aff09e000082ff27",
      "text": ">「チームの心理的安全性」という概念を最初に提唱したのは、ハーバード大学で組織行動学を研究するエイミー エドモンソン氏です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556087898,
      "updated": 1556087899
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc0045daff09e000082ff28",
      "text": "\tsee [Psychological Safety and Learning Behavior in Work Teams]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556087902,
      "updated": 1556087908
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc00026aff09e000082ff11",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556086824,
      "updated": 1556086824
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc0011baff09e000082ff16",
      "text": "\t心理的安全性",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556087068,
      "updated": 1556087077
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc00124aff09e000082ff1f",
      "text": "\t\t対人関係においてリスクある行動を取っても大丈夫だと信じられるかどうか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556087077,
      "updated": 1556087095
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc00137aff09e000082ff20",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556087095,
      "updated": 1556087104
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc0011baff09e000082ff18",
      "text": "\t相互信頼: ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556087068,
      "updated": 1556087119
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc0014faff09e000082ff21",
      "text": "\t\tクオリティの高い仕事を時間内に仕上げるか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556087119,
      "updated": 1556087128
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc0011baff09e000082ff19",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556087068,
      "updated": 1556087068
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc0011baff09e000082ff1a",
      "text": "\t構造と明確さ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556087068,
      "updated": 1556087136
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc00160aff09e000082ff22",
      "text": "\t\t職務上で要求されていることと要求を満たすプロセスが理解されていること",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556087136,
      "updated": 1556087169
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc0011baff09e000082ff1b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556087068,
      "updated": 1556087068
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc0011baff09e000082ff1c",
      "text": "\t仕事の意味",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556087068,
      "updated": 1556087173
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc00184aff09e000082ff23",
      "text": "\t\t仕事の成果に対してメンバーが主観的に意味を感じられるかどうか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556087173,
      "updated": 1556087244
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc00185aff09e000082ff24",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556087174,
      "updated": 1556087192
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc0011baff09e000082ff1e",
      "text": "\tインパクト",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556087068,
      "updated": 1556087198
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc0019eaff09e000082ff25",
      "text": "\t\t個人の仕事が組織の目標達成に貢献していること",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556087198,
      "updated": 1556087235
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc001c2aff09e000082ff26",
      "text": "\t\t個人の仕事のインパクト",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556087235,
      "updated": 1556087240
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc02c79aff09e00005ee43d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556098170,
      "updated": 1556098170
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc02c79aff09e00005ee43e",
      "text": "それぞれのファクターが具体的にどういう方法(アンケート文)で計測されたのか知りたいけど、しばらく探してみても見つけられなかった。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556098170,
      "updated": 1556098214
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc02c82aff09e00005ee440",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556098179,
      "updated": 1556098179
    }
  ]
}